      <title>伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡袭击船只，破坏恢复交通的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/world/middleeast/iran-strait-of-hormuz-threat-rubio-bahrain.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和伊朗官员证实了这次袭击事件，此前德黑兰威胁要扰乱该水道的航运，而华盛顿则为其和平协议寻求地区支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/world/middleeast/iran-strait-of-hormuz-threat-rubio-bahrain.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:14:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院通过 TPS 和南部边境决定扩大特朗普对移民的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/us/politics/supreme-court-temporary-protected-status.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法院让特朗普总统在推动废除对数十万人的驱逐保护并拒绝南部边境的移民方面取得了胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/us/politics/supreme-court-temporary-protected-status.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:10:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大边境收紧限制美国被驱逐者寻求庇护</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/world/canada/canada-border-immigration-deportation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的新政策以及与美国的长期边界协议将使叙利亚人和海地人向北前进变得艰难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/world/canada/canada-border-immigration-deportation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 21:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院扩大特朗普的移民权力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/briefing/supreme-court-trump-immigration.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此外，伊朗还袭击了霍尔木兹海峡的一艘船只。这是周四月底的最新消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/25/briefing/supreme-court-trump-immigration.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 21:34:19 GMT</pubDate>
